1.13
log
@use file system path (.Pa) semantic markup macros where appropriate.

ok jmc@@
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: kbd.8,v 1.12 2009/05/06 19:13:26 jmc Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 1996 Juergen Hannken-Illjes
.\" All rights reserved.
